/nija-bot
│
├── .env                  # Your environment variables (Coinbase JWT info, etc.)
├── requirements.txt      # Python dependencies: loguru, python-dotenv, requests, etc.
├── start_bot.py          # Root-level entry point for Railway
├── nija_client.py        # Your CoinbaseClient wrapper / helper
└── app                   # Optional folder for organizing extra code
    ├── __init__.py       # Makes `app` a Python package
    └── start_bot_module.py  # The main bot logic (optional
